metadata.description: AsciiPunk #1 is a tribute to [CryptoPunk #1](https://opensea.io/assets/0xb47e3cd837ddf8e4c57f05d70ab865de6e193bbb/1). You can check out [AsciiPunk #1's profile and read his interview](https://ascii-museum.com/?page_id=10321) which covers the topics of Metavers, cryptocurrencies, NFTs... On the [Ascii-Museum website](https://ascii-museum.com) you can compare him to other [AsciiPunk](https://ascii-museum.com/asciipunks) via his metadatas and deduce his rarity. He answered these 5 Questions: [Punks are dead?](https://ascii-museum.com?cat=77) [What is the future of Dogecoin(DOGE)?](https://ascii-museum.com?cat=76) [What is the most popular punk band in the world?](https://ascii-museum.com?cat=92) [What do I need BlockChain technology for?](https://ascii-museum.com?cat=112) [Can painting be an NFT?](https://ascii-museum.com?cat=85).
